quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,94,"Chisimu pamasile paŵakusenye ŵanganyao pakwamanya chenene, ni ŵaŵalasile chiŵalanjilo chakwana."
  19,95,"Soni ŵosope ŵeneo tachim’bichilila (Allah) lisiku lya Kiyama jikajika."
  19,96,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji tachaŵichila ŵanganyao chinonyelo."
  20,76,"Matimbe Gandamo, sulo sikujilima cha pasi pakwe, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo, soni galakwega ni malipilo gamundu jwaliswejesye."
  20,77,"Soni chisimu chene Uwwe twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Ŵigulani lwachilo ni achikapolo Ŵangu, ni mwapanjile litala lyejumu m’mbwani, nkajogopa kamulwa (ni Firiauna) soni nkaŵa ni woga (uliose mpela kumilwa).”"
  20,78,"Sano Firiauna ni asilikali ŵakwe ŵakuyiye ŵanganyao, basi ni gaunichiile m’mbwanimo (mesi) gagaakutiiche."
  21,52,"Pandema jaŵaŵechete kwa babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “Ana niyapi ayi isanamu yankuŵa jenumanja nchijendelechelaga kuigalagatila?”"
  21,53,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Twasimene achatati ŵetu achiigalagatilaga.”"
  21,54,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chisimu chene jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu m’bele mukusokonechela kwakuonechela.”"
  22,28,"“Kuti ajise kulola yakwakamuchisya yao, ni kulikolanga Lina lya Allah m’moŵa gakumanyika,   pa yaŵapele ŵanganyao mu inyama yakulanga,   basi lyagani jine mujalakwe (nyamajo), nikwalisya soni ŵayakanganiche ŵaali ŵakulaga.”",footnotes:1:Moŵa gakumanyika gakwe ni aga: pa 10, pa 11, pa 12 ni pa 13 mwesi wa Mfungotatu.,footnotes:2:Inyama yakwe mpela ngamiya, ng’ombe, ngondolo ni mbusi, pakuisikita kuŵa mbepesi kwa Allah, ni kuŵecheta ndema jakuisikitajo kuti: Bismillah [Mulina lya Allah], Wallâhu-Akbar [Soni Allah ni Jwankulunga nnope], Allâhumma Minka wa Ilaika [E Allah! Chinyamachi chiumiile Kukwenu soni chikuja Kukwenu].
  22,29,"“Kaneko aliswejesye ku usakwa wao (pakuwula nguwo sya Ihrâm ni kumyola umbo, kulengula ngose, kupakala mauta gakununjila ni ine), ni kwanilisya nasili syao, nikujisyungula Nyumba jakalakala (Likaaba).”"
  22,30,"Yalakweyo (ni ibada ya Hija yakuŵajilwa ŵandu kuntendela Allah), sano jwataichimbichisye ichindu yakuchimbichika ya Allah, basi (kutenda) yalakweyo tiiŵe yambone kukwakwe pameso pa M’mbujegwe. Ni iŵele halaal kukwenu (kulya) ilango, ikaŵeje yaikusoomedwa kukwenu (mu Qur’an kuti yaharaam). Basi uŵambalani usakwa (wagalagatila) isanamu, soni gaŵambalani maloŵe gaunami."
  23,4,"Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkutenda yakutola Zaka."
  23,5,"Ni aŵala ŵaakuŵa nkuugosa utukani wao."
  23,6,"Ikaŵeje (akuukamulichisya masengo) pa achiŵammakwao kapena yagapatile makono gao gakun’dyo (mateka), basi chisimu ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵagambidwa."